title: kaumah.github.io
body: You are already here! This is my personal website, which has recently been converted entirely to react, and is based on create-react-app. It is meant not only to showcase what I have been working on, but also to experiment with React and other packages.

title: Youtube Uploader Clone
body: This is a barebones YouTube Uploading client that I made in order to get familiar with implementing OAuth2 along with Google sign in. It allows a user to create, view, update, and delete basic attributes of a video.
